{"tid":1671034,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【加泰集會】中國撿到槍： 藉 ‘加泰示威’， 王毅 批西方 「撐香港」是「偽善」。","createTime":"2019-10-23T08:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:38:06.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c03c7b9ba532727d11acf7569900b76d1eb9a35","tid":1671034,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"時間：2019-10-23 11:02<br />\n新聞引據：採訪、法新社<br />\n<br />\n歐洲和南美相繼發生暴力示威抗爭活動，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國抓住這個機會，提升對香港爭民主運動的譴責</span></strong>，並為自己的處理方式辯護。<br />\n<br />\n最近在智利以及西班牙加泰隆尼亞地區的衝突，讓中國增添柴火<strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\">批評西方政府在譴責自己國內暴力的同時，卻<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">虛偽</span>的支持香港的示威</span></strong>。中國國營媒體和官員積極關注最近幾天在外國發生的動亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2018/03/11/20180308000081M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F20180308000081M.jpg&h=1c82e628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部長王毅21日告訴法新社：「我們看到今天在香港發生的暴力，在其它地方被複製。」他<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別點出在加泰隆尼亞</span></span></strong>、智利以及倫敦等地的示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n王毅說：「在加泰隆尼亞，他們公開宣稱第二個香港將在加泰隆尼亞出現，他們是被(香港)發生的事鼓動。我認為，有些人必須思考他們的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n在香港的抗爭行動中，中國以「類似恐怖主義份子」來譴責少數暴力示威者，並譴責外國政府煽動香港的動亂。"},{"pid":"a7c0f3cb36267c70c80a29193ec5ec69235fe8b6","tid":1671034,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:54:57.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2038840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2038840&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2ce7e7b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2038840</a>"},{"pid":"d982adf40010e5b01938fddc5707a55de6ec7ff4","tid":1671034,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"乜智利算係西方國家黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋智利都無出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69e6ec8d6f6b0e7f202d38844206e596bbd8456","tid":1671034,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2475000/2479203/WEB_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2475000%2F2479203%2FWEB_600.png&h=4c87a52b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e165c500e399fe9bdf527d33d294bd782088403","tid":1671034,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0eb6859e02dc7b9e518cc2bd7c66e53fc01b988","tid":1671034,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"來來去去咪美國勢力,用加泰又想入美國數冇野呀"},{"pid":"bb01b544aed273871005fdf25ca4d646d1e5d94a","tid":1671034,"uid":289021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"學咩人講雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講南京大屠殺唔講六四"},{"pid":"b3fdf2ce06f4d331ccf75461ca4b9475dc878ab9","tid":1671034,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:01:53.000Z","msg":"［行動］星期四搵其他地方搞全球反警暴集會！<br />\n並強調參加撐加泰集會嘅都係五毛扮反送中人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1670501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1670501</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6510ffe107696bfe3726eee2b1a2464e8fb5828","tid":1671034,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"將大粒癦單嘢發大嚟搞，拖機管局、民航處、航空公司落水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"118bb5c73584381aa93ce8dac4a003827b305fd3","tid":1671034,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"